{"tid":987732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安定邨男子燒炭　送院不治","createTime":"2019-01-19T14:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T16:31:33.000Z","uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a1275fa45488d1bbe0d4cd379f120433a22eef6b","tid":987732,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"屯門安定邨定德樓，凌晨約3時，一名姓谷女子(42歲)走到姓曾男友(45歲)家中，發現有煙滲出，拍門無人應，連忙報警求助。消防員到場破門入屋，證實男事主昏迷，即時將他送屯門醫院搶救，惜告不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方撿獲燒炭器皿及炭灰，相信男事主燒炭輕生，經調查得悉他有金錢問題，事件沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190119/59159719\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190119%2F59159719&d=zWG2U%2B41zKINFbZZZjzGWzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c5868c0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190119%2F59159719&h=b10d3525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190119/59159719</a>"},{"pid":"70a7779742945f30fbe24b79440d60014303cbe3","tid":987732,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5585f5145e5bf48022e051f88497f11524c6d32","tid":987732,"uid":10692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d78137be08b035960b1e614e190a9cafab670e6a","tid":987732,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:24:55.000Z","msg":"奶波魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fc9070771b2941fbc58109aebf65ab9cd27442","tid":987732,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"公屋仔的命運"},{"pid":"257a944f250e0c637dc073983851332c01257534","tid":987732,"uid":212317,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cit